    {
      "id": "696ac7d600000000003ab6c4",
      "text": "\t[回転寿司]のページ見てて思いついた[笑い声]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1768605656,
      "updated": 1768605670
    },
    {
      "id": "696ac7e400000000003ab6c5",
      "text": "\t\t「[すしし]」",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1768605670,
      "updated": 1768607722
    },
    {
      "id": "696ac7e500000000003ab6c6",
      "text": "\t[妄想踏みゲー]をつくって遊んでいる",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1768605671,
      "updated": 1768615483
    },
    {
      "id": "696ac80c00000000003ab6c8",
      "text": "\t\t[エキセントリックコンコン #DDS #DanceDanceShuffle - YouTube https://www.youtube.com/shorts/hDpO7SiW94U]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1768605710,
      "updated": 1768605710
    },
    {
      "id": "696ac82000000000003ab6c9",
      "text": "\t\t[運動の自作と習慣的実践]だ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1768605730,
      "updated": 1768605732
    },
    {
      "id": "696ac80200000000003ab6c7",
      "text": "\t[妄想音ゲー]の概念がたぶん難しい",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1768605700,
      "updated": 1768615481
    },
    {
      "id": "696acf9c00000000002bf844",
      "text": "\t\t例: [昔遊んでた「妄想音ゲー」 - YouTube https://www.youtube.com/shorts/oSnUlhFOU7g]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1768607647,
      "updated": 1768607648
    },
    {
      "id": "696acf9600000000002bf843",
      "text": "\t米が贅沢品または嗜好品になりつつある",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1768607640,
      "updated": 1768613748
    },
    {
      "id": "696ae77200000000008ccef1",
      "text": "\t\t2kgで3000円！（3倍）",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1768613748,
      "updated": 1768614145
    },
    {
      "id": "696ae77600000000008ccef2",
      "text": "\t\t1合食べるとしても1食230円かかるよ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1768613752,
      "updated": 1768613762
    },
    {
      "id": "696ae78a00000000008ccef3",
      "text": "\t\t肉（安い鶏肉でも100g150円くらいはする）や野菜も考えると、自炊でも1食400円する時代になってきたわけか",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1768613772,
      "updated": 1768613800
    },
    {
      "id": "696ae7a800000000008ccef4",
      "text": "\t\tつらたん",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1768613802,
      "updated": 1768613803
    },
    {
      "id": "696ae94e00000000008ccef5",
      "text": "\t\t米離れに投資した方がいいのかもなぁ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1768614224,
      "updated": 1768614230
    },
    {
      "id": "696ae95a00000000008ccef6",
      "text": "\t\t給料上げれば一番だけどニューロダイバシティ次第なのでどうしようもないしなー",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1768614237,
      "updated": 1768614251
    },
    {
      "id": "696ae76900000000008ccef0",
      "text": "\tじょうほうしゅうしゅう",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1768613739,
      "updated": 1768634987
    },
    {
      "id": "696b3a6b00000000002801c0",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/a1f8f3a58e322b8dc786760df6a0ed37]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1768634987,
      "updated": 1768634988
    },
    {
      "id": "696b3a6700000000002801bf",
